# Basic Memory schema notes — use BM-specific notation ([category], [[wiki-links]])
# that remark's no-undefined-references rule cannot parse.
schemas/

# Sprint retrospectives — gitignored, local-only, use BM-style [category] prose
# and >NN constructs that trip no-undefined-references / no-blockquote-without-marker.
RETRO-*.md

# Swarm-wave sprint state — gitignored, ephemeral scratch; agent-assignment lines
# use [P1]/[P2]/[P3] priority tags that remark reads as undefined link references.
SWARM-*.md

# Plan / design working drafts — gitignored, local-only; same bracket-prose hazard.
PLAN-*.md
